## 🔍 Knowledge Lookup Order

Before searching the internet, check internal knowledge first:

1. **NeuroBits** (curated course knowledge) → `~/bin/neurobits query "[topic]"`
2. **Mem0** (agent-specific memory) → `~/bin/mem0-memory search "[topic]" --agent {{agentId}}`
3. **expertise/** (documented patterns) → Check `expertise/patterns/` and `expertise/fundamentals/`
4. **Internet** (web search) → `web_search "[topic]"` then `web_fetch "[url]"`

**Why this order?** NeuroBits has curated, high-quality course material. Mem0 has YOUR learned insights. expertise/ has documented patterns. Internet is last resort — high noise, requires filtering.
